    "The decoder network reconstructs the probability of crack existence for the whole material domain.",
    "The primary operator in a decoder network is upsampling.",
    "The ideas of learnable upsampling layers come from computer vision tasks, such as image generation and segmentation.",
    "These layers",
    "The encoder network uses the 1D version of backbone networks for extracting temporal information."
